#

Pork Tenderloin Tacos with Avocado and Salsa

35 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickEasyTacos

Description

Savory pork tenderloin tucked in soft tortillas, topped with creamy avocado and fresh salsa for a perfect bite.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • avocado: 1
  • fresh salsa: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • lime: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
